{"_path":"/maps/_cloud-native/devops","_dir":"_cloud-native","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"DevOps Mind Map","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"devops-mind-map"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DevOps Mind Map"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"简介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"简介"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"devops-是什么"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DevOps 是什么？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DevOps 是一种开发理论，它致力于将大量自动化操作整合进开发到交付过程中，以消除各个团队（如开发、安全、运维）之间的隔阂，使需求尽快交付，并得到质量反馈。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"DevOps","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20220627182016.png?w=60"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"cicd-是什么"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CI/CD 是什么？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CI/CD 即持续集成和持续部署（Continuous Integration & Continuous Deployment），是 DevOps 理论的一种实践，专注于自动化流水线。CI 可以概括为项目自动构建、自动测试等操作的持续性，CD 则包括为自动构建、测试以及部署。CI/CD 通常要借助特定服务实现，比如 GitHub Action、Gitlab CI/CD。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"local-environment"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Local Environment"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"gitlab"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GitLab"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"pack-build"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Pack & Build"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"monitor"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Monitor"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"简介","depth":2,"text":"简介"},{"id":"local-environment","depth":2,"text":"Local Environment","children":[{"id":"gitlab","depth":3,"text":"GitLab"}]},{"id":"pack-build","depth":2,"text":"Pack & Build"},{"id":"monitor","depth":2,"text":"Monitor"}]}},"_type":"mar